    "title": "Hiring Medical Officer at LV Prasad Eye Institute",
    "description": "LV Prasad Eye Institute, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Medical Officer for our Navi Mumbai operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout LV Prasad Eye Institute:\nLV Prasad Eye Institute is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Participate in quality improvement initiatives and clinical audits\n• Monitor patient progress and adjust treatment plans accordingly\n• Attend continuing medical education programs and training\n• Conduct routine health assessments and screenings\n• Administer medications and treatments as prescribed\n• Adhere to NABH/JCI accreditation standards\n• Maintain sterile environments and follow infection control protocols\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Medical Coding\n• Proficiency in Medical Terminology\n• Proficiency in EMR/EHR\n• Proficiency in Infection Control\n• Proficiency in BLS/ACLS\n• Proficiency in Telemedicine\n• Proficiency in Clinical Documentation\n• Proficiency in Pharmacovigilance\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Referral bonus program\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Navi Mumbai, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with LV Prasad Eye Institute!",
